STATE
v.
James David NANNEY. No. 357P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Dec. 15, 2015. Harriet F. Worley, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. James David Nanney, pro, Maury, for Nanney, James David. Todd Williams, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

*570The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd of October 2015 by Defendant for Notice of Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed Ex Mero Motu by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of December 2015."
